{"tid":643612,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】鹽與聖所 + 到時想玩嘅Game Day201 26/4","createTime":"2018-04-26T15:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T17:41:48.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6da705719101d4583894c8ef0156206adc9438b1","tid":643612,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T15:25:49.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=g0rGYIVa9wBzMQsZpoCyfviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=17f0bfcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=g0rGYIVa9wBzMQsZpoCyfviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=ac6bd538\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"b0f3f870a8c13daf774e0297456c886ec0b3730b","tid":643612,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T15:27:02.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd23debe81e61eff5d74d54d255eae5a5d6c297","tid":643612,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T15:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c623ec5354f7496538304fc4a7fd723c1ab99521","tid":643612,